{
  "video_id": "2N3XqyuOwIM",
  "title": "The Explainer: Blue Ocean Strategy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 8520.0,
      "end_time": 11709.0,
      "text": "In 1984, Guy Laliberte cofounded Cirque du Soleil."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 11710.0,
      "end_time": 14460.0,
      "text": "Soon, Cirque was bringing in revenues that incumbents like"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14460.0,
      "end_time": 17480.0,
      "text": "Ringling Brothers had taken more than a century to attain --"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17480.0,
      "end_time": 20500.0,
      "text": "even though the circus business was in long-term decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20500.0,
      "end_time": 23800.0,
      "text": "How did Cirque thrive in such a dismal environment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23800.0,
      "end_time": 25710.0,
      "text": "The answer can be found in the theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25710.0,
      "end_time": 27640.0,
      "text": "that the business universe consists"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27640.0,
      "end_time": 31700.0,
      "text": "of two kinds of markets: red oceans and blue oceans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31700.0,
      "end_time": 35130.0,
      "text": "a concept pioneered by INSEAD professors W. Chan Kim"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35130.0,
      "end_time": 36730.0,
      "text": "and Renee Mauborgne."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36730.0,
      "end_time": 39830.0,
      "text": "Red oceans represent existing industries and markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39830.0,
      "end_time": 42150.0,
      "text": "where industry boundaries and the rules of competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42150.0,
      "end_time": 43240.0,
      "text": "are well-defined."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43240.0,
      "end_time": 45780.0,
      "text": "Companies strive to outperform rivals and grab a bigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45780.0,
      "end_time": 47590.0,
      "text": "share of existing demand."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47590.0,
      "end_time": 50300.0,
      "text": "As the space gets crowded, fierce competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50300.0,
      "end_time": 51450.0,
      "text": "turns the water bloody."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51450.0,
      "end_time": 54110.0,
      "text": "Competitive or market-competing strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54110.0,
      "end_time": 57110.0,
      "text": "is about how to occupy red oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57110.0,
      "end_time": 60850.0,
      "text": "By contrast, blue ocean or market-creating strategy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60850.0,
      "end_time": 63900.0,
      "text": "is about how to create and capture unknown markets where"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63900.0,
      "end_time": 66679.0,
      "text": "demand is created rather than fought over."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66680.0,
      "end_time": 70150.0,
      "text": "In some cases, this spawns entirely new industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70150.0,
      "end_time": 73590.0,
      "text": "But most blue oceans emerge when a company alters the boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73590.0,
      "end_time": 76540.0,
      "text": "of an existing industry, as when Cirque du Soleil blurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76540.0,
      "end_time": 78950.0,
      "text": "the line between circus and theatre."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78950.0,
      "end_time": 82400.0,
      "text": "Cirque made the acts more artistic and sophisticated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82400.0,
      "end_time": 84430.0,
      "text": "attracting a whole new group of customers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84430.0,
      "end_time": 87200.0,
      "text": "adults who were prepared to pay premium ticket prices as they"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87200.0,
      "end_time": 89220.0,
      "text": "would for theater or the opera."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89220.0,
      "end_time": 91550.0,
      "text": "Cirque also eliminated several elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91550.0,
      "end_time": 94530.0,
      "text": "of the traditional circus like costly animal acts and star"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94530.0,
      "end_time": 95720.0,
      "text": "performers."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95720.0,
      "end_time": 98700.0,
      "text": "Cirque invented a new and profitable market space"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98700.0,
      "end_time": 100360.0,
      "text": "without making the typical tradeoff"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100360.0,
      "end_time": 102130.0,
      "text": "between value and cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102130.0,
      "end_time": 105699.0,
      "text": "Cirque pursued both differentiation and low cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105700.0,
      "end_time": 108360.0,
      "text": "in what Kim and Mauborgne call \"value innovation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 108360.0,
      "end_time": 111340.0,
      "text": "The simultaneous pursuit of value and cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111340.0,
      "end_time": 113610.0,
      "text": "is the logic of blue ocean strategy."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113610.0,
      "end_time": 116440.0,
      "text": "Based on their study of more than thirty industries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116440.0,
      "end_time": 118520.0,
      "text": "companies that can create blue oceans"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118520.0,
      "end_time": 121369.0,
      "text": "usually reap the benefits for 10 to 15 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121370.0,
      "end_time": 123720.0,
      "text": "because they are hard for rivals to copy."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123720.0,
      "end_time": 126590.0,
      "text": "To realize blue ocean potential, like Cirque did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126590.0,
      "end_time": 128830.0,
      "text": "companies should chart a strategic course"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128830.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130710.00000000001,
      "text": "past traditional industry boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130710.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133510.0,
      "text": "to create new market space."
    }
  ]
}